===========================
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Length: 84
Content-Type: application/json
Fiware-Correlator: REGEX([0-9a-f\-]{36})
Date: REGEX(.*)

{
    "id": "Room1",
    "temperature": {
        "metadata": {},
        "type": "Float",
        "value": 23
    },
    "type": "Room"
}


